metadata.name: You Get Nothing - AI The Artist Feat. Not Drake & Pauly
metadata.description:
On May 30th, 2023, Pauly (@Pauly0x) dropped a tweet demanding ETH. It wasn't some pre-sale or token thing, nah, it was for absolutely anything. And guess what? The GIF attached to the tweet was like, "You Get Nothing."

Within a freaking day, Pauly was staring at a wallet stuffed with over a million bucks. YouGetNothing.eth started spreading like wildfire on crypto Twitter, and it ain't slowing down. Right now, Pauly's wallet is almost hitting the 2-million-dollar mark. Talk about ballin'!

And that's how this sick song was born. It's a song about nada, zilch, zero, you name it. It's so lit that words can't even describe how much of a void it represents.

I'm all about the memes, the buzz, and the drama, so I whipped up this track in just 30 minutes and dropped it the next day for the community to vibe with. Now, you can get your own piece of nothingness on the blockchain.

Oh, and here's the kicker: I've decided that 50% of the profits from this NFT will go straight to YouGetNothing.eth. But here's the best partâ€”it's only gonna cost you a dollar! Yeah, you heard that right. You can snag this Music NFT for just one buck and get absolutely nothing in return. Crazy, right?
